    "An intermediate pruning of the tree would decrease the memory requirements to the point where support for distributed parallelism may be redundant.",
    "Since S 3 is designed to compress large amounts of volume data, it is unsuited for surface data applications.",
    "In this case, the octree mesh cannot accurately represent the surface contour, leading to high interpolation errors when exporting the flow fields onto the grid created by S 3.",
    "These errors are caused by the KNN interpolation and may be pronounced near thin geometries, such as the trailing edge of an airfoil.",
    "However, for the test cases shown here, the error remains within acceptable bounds."
